Files in  /opt/info/courses/OpenGL/tutor:

OpenGL Tutorial programs by nate Robins.

NOTE: programs must be be run from within this directory in order to access
model data.

fog
	demonstrates fog

lightmaterial
	demonstrates light and material properites

lightposition
	demonstrates positioning the light source

projection
	demonstrates changing viewing/projection parameters

texture
	demonstrates texturing

transformation
	demonstrates sequences of transformations

data/
	object data

dist/
	original distribution

Please address queries to toby.howard@manchester.ac.uk

[ends]
